ommended if these drugs are coadministered with insulin, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/300681/', '', '', '', 1767369485);
