ed if these drugs are coadministered with insulin, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/300701/', '', 'Trimethoprim, Sorbitol, Sodium citrate, Magnesium citrate, Mannitol, Sodium bicarbonate, Sodium chloride, Chlorhexidine, Neomycin, Tamsulosin, Tinidazole, More', '', 1767369485);
